UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'Home of AWS Mexico (Central) Region, mx-central-1. The first AWS cloud region in Mexico, built to deliver low-latency cloud services across the country and nearby markets.' WHERE id = 'queretaro';

UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'My current city, where my AWS and tech journey continue to grow. You can usually find me at The Lab downtown in the Palm Tower Suites working on my tech game. Don''t sleep on Sarasota. This is the home of the Sarasota.Tech community, launched with no marketing budget and fueled entirely by word of mouth, it has exploded from a handful of friends to more than 3,000 builders, founders, and cloud professionals in just two years. Sarasota isn''t just a beach town anymore, it''s becoming a launchpad for modern, cloud-native innovation. Nearby Tampa, FL is also an AWS Data Center Edge Location.' WHERE id = 'sarasota';

UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'Home of Hudl, one of the most widely used SaaS video platforms in sports. Hudl provides cloud-based video analysis, film review, and recruiting tools for coaches and athletes at every level, from youth leagues to the NFL. I spent over a decade on the platform, breaking down game film and evaluating high school recruiting video from the cloud long before "cloud-based workflows" became a buzzword in the tech world. Hudl was my first real experience with SaaS video technology, I just didn''t know to call it that yet.' WHERE id = 'omaha';

UPDATE cities SET connection_description = 'The capital city of Colombia and a rising tech hub where government, business, and cloud infrastructure are converging. In 2019, AWS activated its first Latin American edge location outside of Brazil right here in Bogotá. Today Bogotá hosts an AWS Local Zone (us-east-1-bog-1a), tethered to the US East (N. Virginia) parent region, bringing compute, storage, and low-latency services directly to Colombian businesses and developers. In 2023, AWS also opened a Direct Connect location inside the Equinix BG1 data center in Bogotá, enabling private, high-speed connections between AWS and local enterprise networks. Also home to Liftit, a leading SaaS logistics and last-mile delivery platform built in Colombia and expanding across Latin America.' WHERE id = 'bogota';